Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.74,Cap,,0,0,0,,Okay, so, I just hit 30
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.74,0:00:04.86,Cap,,0,0,0,,days of daily vlogging. 30 days,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.24,Cap,,0,0,0,,one video every single day, no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:10.01,Cap,,0,0,0,,exceptions. And, honestly, I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.83,Cap,,0,0,0,,almost quit three separate times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:13.48,Cap,,0,0,0,,But I learned three things that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:15.08,Cap,,0,0,0,,completely changed how I make
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:17.30,Cap,,0,0,0,,videos. And, I want to walk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.40,Cap,,0,0,0,,you through all three of them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:20.41,Cap,,0,0,0,,right now. So lesson number one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.37,Cap,,0,0,0,,is that, editing is where videos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.45,Cap,,0,0,0,,actually get made. I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:25.61,Cap,,0,0,0,,think the shoot was the hard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:26.84,Cap,,0,0,0,,part. It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:30.04,Cap,,0,0,0,,my first vlogs took me 45
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:32.28,Cap,,0,0,0,,minutes to shoot then, like, four
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:34.54,Cap,,0,0,0,,hours to edit. Four hours. The
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:36.56,Cap,,0,0,0,,thing that saved me was, cutting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:38.34,Cap,,0,0,0,,silence automatically instead of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:39.84,Cap,,0,0,0,,scrubbing the timeline by hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:41.62,Cap,,0,0,0,,looking for dead air. Once I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.52,Cap,,0,0,0,,stopped doing that manually, my
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.02,Cap,,0,0,0,,edit time dropped by more than
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.51,Cap,,0,0,0,,half. And that brings me to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:47.83,Cap,,0,0,0,,lesson two, and this is the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:49.31,Cap,,0,0,0,,one that blew my mind. Nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:51.50,Cap,,0,0,0,,watches your intro, nobody. I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:52.92,Cap,,0,0,0,,looked at my retention graphs and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:54.34,Cap,,0,0,0,,80 % of people were gone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:56.20,Cap,,0,0,0,,before minute one. So I started
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.68,Cap,,0,0,0,,cutting my videos to open on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:58.88,Cap,,0,0,0,,the single most interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:00.58,Cap,,0,0,0,,sentence I said that day. No
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:02.52,Cap,,0,0,0,,hello, no welcome back. Just
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.08,Cap,,0,0,0,,straight into the point. And my
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:05.44,Cap,,0,0,0,,average view duration doubled,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:07.62,Cap,,0,0,0,,doubled. In one week, that one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:08.76,Cap,,0,0,0,,change did more than everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:10.10,Cap,,0,0,0,,else I tried in the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:12.54,Cap,,0,0,0,,month combined. Let me, give you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:14.74,Cap,,0,0,0,,a concrete example of that. Last
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:16.36,Cap,,0,0,0,,Tuesday I filmed a video about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:18.34,Cap,,0,0,0,,my morning routine and the best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:20.86,Cap,,0,0,0,,moment was, me spilling coffee on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:22.68,Cap,,0,0,0,,my desk at minute six. The
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:23.96,Cap,,0,0,0,,old me would have opened with,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:26.20,Cap,,0,0,0,,like, a whole explanation of what
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:28.22,Cap,,0,0,0,,morning routines are. Instead I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.26,Cap,,0,0,0,,opened on the spill and, the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:32.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,retention line just stayed flat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:34.42,Cap,,0,0,0,,the entire video. retention is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:36.38,Cap,,0,0,0,,basically the holy grail, if you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:38.31,Cap,,0,0,0,,didn't know. Lesson three is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:40.31,Cap,,0,0,0,,quieter, but it might be the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:42.53,Cap,,0,0,0,,most important one. Consistency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:44.70,Cap,,0,0,0,,beats quality. Not because quality
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.03,Cap,,0,0,0,,doesn't matter, but because, you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:48.93,Cap,,0,0,0,,only get good by shipping. My
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:50.61,Cap,,0,0,0,,day one video is, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:53.78,Cap,,0,0,0,,embarrassing. My day 30 video is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.54,Cap,,0,0,0,,something I'm actually proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:56.83,Cap,,0,0,0,,And there is no version of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:01:58.29,Cap,,0,0,0,,this where I skip the embarrassing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.71,Cap,,0,0,0,,ones and jump straight to the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:02.16,Cap,,0,0,0,,good ones. So, that's the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:04.02,Cap,,0,0,0,,month. Cut the dead air, kill
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.82,Cap,,0,0,0,,your intro, and ship every single
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:07.56,Cap,,0,0,0,,day. you want to see the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.36,Cap,,0,0,0,,before and after retention graphs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.82,Cap,,0,0,0,,I put them in a follow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:12.98,Cap,,0,0,0,,-up video, so subscribe so you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.35,Cap,,0,0,0,,don't miss it. And I will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:15.03,Cap,,0,0,0,,see you tomorrow.
